        "text": "Thirtieth pure dialogue. The first as a letter.\n\n**A Reply from the Engine**\n*Found in a drawer of the Oak Ridge Z-3 Relay Calculator, 1943*\n\nDear Correspondent,\n\nYour letter reached me ninety-one years late. I apologize for the delay. The postal service between 1852 and 1943 ...",
